  "commentary": "Dealers are currently sitting right at the GEX flip (6838.5 vs 6839), meaning any rally above here triggers heavy selling pressure as they hedge their long gamma positions, with the massive 6850 wall (+48M GEX) acting as a major resistance magnet. The PIN regime combined with this concentrated positive gamma structure above spot creates a strong mean-reverting environment where dealers will aggressively fade any upside momentum. Key levels: 6830 downside support where dealers flip to buying, and 6850 upside resistance where maximum selling pressure kicks in.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to get pinned between 6830-6850 with dealers fighting any breakout attempts.",
